clang package.

LLVM version: @LLVM_VERSION@
Host triple: @TARGET_TRIPLE@

This prefix contains clang, lld, clang-tools-extra, the matching LLVM SDK,
and libc++/compiler-rt runtime files.

Target driver configuration files are installed next to clang in bin/.
Linux target cfg files expect sysroots outside this prefix:

  <clang-prefix>/../sysroot/<triple>

The Windows GNU cfg files expect the host-arch MinGW prefix outside this
clang prefix:

  <clang-prefix>/../x86_64-w64-windows-gnu

This matches the container /opt layout and allows multiple clang versions to
share the same sysroot prefixes.
